Sentencas: Polycrystalline samples of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-delta (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) (PSFC) were prepared by the combustion synthesis route at 1200 degrees C.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: The structure of the polycrystalline powders was analysed with X-ray powder diffraction data.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: The X-ray diffraction (XRD) patterns were indexed as the orthoferrite similar to that of PrFeO3 having a single-phase orthorhombic perovskite structure (Pbnm).
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-delta (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) films have been deposited on yttria-stabilized zirconia (YSZ)single-crystal substrates at 700 degrees C by pulsed laser deposition (PLD) for application to thin film solid oxide fuel cell cathodes.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: The structure of the films was analysed by XRD, scanning electron microscopy (SEM) and atomic force microscopy (AFM).
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: All films are polycrystalline with a marked texture and present pyramidal grains in the surface with different size distributions.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy (EIS) measurements of PSFC/YSZ single crystal/PSFC test cells were conducted.
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation

Sentencas: The Pr0.7Sr0.3Fe0.8Co0.2O3-delta film at 850 degrees C presents a lower area specific resistance (ASR) value, 1.65 Omega cm(2), followed by the Pr0.8Sr0.2Fe0.8Co0.2O3-delta (2.29 Omega cm(2) at 850 degrees C) and the Pr0.9Sr0.1Fe0.8Co0.2O3-delta films (5.45 Omega cm(2) at 850 degrees C).
Titulo: Structure and impedance spectroscopy of Pr1-xSrxFe0.8Co0.2O3-δ (x=0.1, 0.2, 0.3) thin films grown by laser ablation
